    "Performance was similar in the immunotherapy dataset, which represents a separate but similar patient population treated at the same hospital system.",
    "We observed a performance decrement in the MIMIC-III dataset, representing a more dissimilar patient population from a different hospital system.",
    "Performance was similar between models developed with and without synthetic data.",
